{"word":"G3122 - μάλιστα - málista - mal'-is-tah - Chiefly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μάλιστα</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">málista</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mal'-is-tah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Chiefly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அதிகமாய், விசேஷமாய் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"especially, chiefly, most of all, above all"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter plural of the superlative of an apparently primary adverb <b>&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03B1;</b> <b>mala</b> (<i>very</i>); (adverb) <i>most</i> (<i>in the greatest degree</i>) or <i>particularly:</i> - chiefly, most of all, (e-) specially.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}